{"data":[{"date":"00:22 16/08","title":"Luke Shaw b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3m b\u00e9o","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/luke-shaw-bat-dau-chien-dich-giam-beo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a HLV Mourinho.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Luke Shaw \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh gi\u1ea3m b\u00e9o sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i v\u00ec d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. B\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng l\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi chuy\u00ean gia dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, ki\u00eam \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ebfp Jonny Marsh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Manchester United t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, Shaw \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m v\u00ec th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh to l\u1edbn, kh\u1eafc h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh anh khi m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford. Nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u00e9o ph\u00ec sau qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i b\u1ecb Jose Mourinho \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Shaw \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a sao Man City, Luke Shaw gi\u1ea3m b\u00e9o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a sao Man City, Luke Shaw gi\u1ea3m b\u00e9o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/luke-shaw-noi-gi-sau-khi-ghi-ban-thang-dau-tien-cho-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Leicester City l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Shaw.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City, Luke Shaw \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i v\u00f3c d\u00e1ng, phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Marsh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap anh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng ng\u1ee7 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nShaw ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Marsh t\u1ea1i Anh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ebfp n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kevin de Bruyne, Kyle Walker, Ilkay Gundogan, Maroane Fellaini v\u00e0 John Terry thu\u00ea l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Marsh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn nh\u00e0 Luke Shaw \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ea5u b\u1eefa t\u1ed1i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i ra trong nh\u1eefng n\u00e0y Shaw ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Marsh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eefa \u0103n nh\u1eb9, \u0111\u1ed3 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay Shaw kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t, Jose Mourinho s\u1ebd c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 12 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5537","checkdouble":"194573"},{"date":"19:15 15/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 15/8: V\u00ec Man Utd, Zidane s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eadt k\u00e8o Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/31/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-158-vi-man-utd-zidane-san-sang-lat-keo-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 15/8.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zidane nh\u1eafm gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Man Utd</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 158 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 158 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/ngay-hom-nay-18.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Zinedine Zidane</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia tay Real Madrid tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh vinh quang, Zidane c\u0169ng s\u1ebd s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u1ee5 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Th\u1ec3 thao \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m \u1edf Juventus. Tuy nhi\u00ean, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eadt k\u00e8o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man Utd v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m sau. Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng HLV c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho \u0111ang lung lay d\u1eef d\u1ed9i \u1edf Old Trafford b\u1edfi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sarri ghi th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng \u1edf Chelsea<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 158 V\u00ec Man Utd, Zidane s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eadt k\u00e8o Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 158 V\u00ec Man Utd, Zidane s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eadt k\u00e8o Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-158-Vi-Man-Utd,-Zidane-san-sang-lat-keo-Juventus-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Maurizio Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi th\u1ed5i v\u00e0o Stamford Bridge, Maurizio Sarri d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u1edbi \u1edf Chelsea, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t so v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Antonio Conte. Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1edbi l\u1ecfng ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 \u00edt kh\u1eaft khe h\u01a1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f3i quen tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn MU \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean v\u00ec Pogba <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba vo dich the gioi\" title=\"Pogba v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/chu-tich-barca-chua-tu-bo-y-dinh-cuom-pogba-khoi-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Paul Pogba</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tranh th\u1ee7 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p gi\u1eefa Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Jose Mourinho c\u00f9ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n chia tay Man Utd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, Barcelona l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y. Sau ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu th\u00ec G\u0110TT Ariedo Braida c\u0169ng \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cu\u1ed7m ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t Old Trafford v\u1ec1 Camp Nou, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 danh t\u00ednh nh\u1eb1m t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u00e1c CLB kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chia tay ng\u00f4i sao ti\u1ebfp theo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Drinkwater\" title=\"Drinkwater\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/26/drinkwater-vua-mac-phai-sai-lam-lon-nhat-doi-minh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Danny Drinkwater</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Mateo Kovacic v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e8 l\u00e0 Jorginho, tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 k\u00e9o theo, t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch d\u1ecdn d\u1eb9p thanh l\u00fd trong th\u00e1ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y. Sau khi Tiemoue Bakayoko \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Milan, Danny Drinkwater c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo ph\u1ea3i chia tay Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sao Man Utd cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u1edf Old Trafford<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Herrera\" title=\"Herrera\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ander Herrera</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng Ander Herrera c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u00edt lo l\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i \u1edf. T\u00ecnh y\u00eau Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 x\u1ee9 Basque l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i v\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 d\u00e0i l\u00e2u v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Chuy\u1ec7n gia h\u1ea1n d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a HLV v\u00e0 BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sao Liverpool chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb gia nh\u1eadp Napoli<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Mignolet\" title=\"thu mon Mignolet\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/20/Vuot-mat-Barca,-Napoli-muon-mua-Simon-Mignolet-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Simon Mignolet</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 Alisson Becker v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Loris Karius c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng h\u01a1n cho vai tr\u00f2 k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong khung g\u1ed7 Anfield cho Simon Mignolet g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, thay v\u00ec b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 danh gi\u00e1 Barcelona th\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Napoli n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef v\u1ec1 m\u00e1i nh\u00e0 m\u1edbi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"San moi cua Tottenham dang trong qua trinh hoan thien va du kien mo cua vao ngay 15/9.\" title=\"S\u00e2n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn m\u1edf c\u1eeda v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-he-2018-Mua-khong-noi,-ban-chang-xong!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>S\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Tottenham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Tottenham d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1nh th\u00e0nh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng Ch\u00edn t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ngay trong m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u00ec m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do hay s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 ngo\u00e0i \u00fd mu\u1ed1n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t cho t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng M\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ed9t. Trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, Spurs s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Wembley l\u00e0m s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5536","checkdouble":"194555"},{"date":"21:18 15/08","title":"Real Madrid 2-4 Atletico: \"Ma c\u0169\" b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t \"ma m\u1edbi\", Atletico l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/15/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t Diego Simeone qu\u00e1 gi\u00e0 d\u01a1 v\u00e0 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i n\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba chi\u00eau th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c m\u1ed9t Lopetegui m\u1edbi l\u00e0m thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf CLB m\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 CLB kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 \u0111\u00eam qua. Atletico m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o 30 ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 2-2 \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i tung ra 2 \u0111\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1 knock-out ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng.</h2><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u1edf m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, Real Madrid ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.  Sau m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ec7ch cho\u1ea1c khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man United \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n  International Champions Cup 2018, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n  l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Juventus v\u00e0 Roma. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Real Madrid ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i AC Milan v\u1edbi  t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh Bernabeu Trophy. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m  \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Atletico Madrid doat Sieu cup chau Au sau 120 phut chien dau voi Real\" title=\"Atletico Madrid \u0111o\u1ea1t Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u sau 120 ph\u00fat chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/1017288804_18685.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Atletico Madrid \u0111o\u1ea1t Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u sau 120 ph\u00fat chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; n\u00e0o trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay,  nh\u01b0ng HLV Lopetegui d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n  gi\u1ea3n, Real th\u1eddi h\u1eadu Ronaldo v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh c\u1ef1c \u1ed5n. Trong khi Real Madrid kh\u00e1  th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay th\u00ec Atletico Madrid ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n  tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 5 tr\u1eadn t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1 tr\u1eadn (thua 2, h\u00f2a 2).  Trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf International Champions Cup 2018. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3,  Atletico b\u1ecb PSG \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 3-2 v\u00e0 thua Inter 0-1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Atletico \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 r\u1ea7m r\u1ed9. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng  cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nikola Kalinic (c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng  kh\u1eafp World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i khi b\u1ecb tuy\u1ec3n Croatia \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n  ra v\u00ec v\u00f4 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt), ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rodrigo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Thomas Lemar  t\u1eeb Monaco. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m v\u1eeba qua, c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a  Atletico \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi.\r\n<p>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tranh danh hi\u1ec7u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o  ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i tung ra l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. B\u00ean ph\u00eda Real, HLV Lopetegui  ch\u1eb3ng d\u00e1m m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m m\u00e0 v\u1eabn tin d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ef1u binh c\u1ee7a tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ngay c\u1ea3  th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh Courtois v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i  d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Navas. Hay nh\u01b0 Odriozola, c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Lopetegui \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb TBN  (ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 n\u00e0y v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0110TQG tham d\u1ef1 World Cup  2018), c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i b\u1edfi ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 s\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Dani Carvajal \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed  h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Costa\" title=\"Diego Costa\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/4F1F5D5F00000578-6064435-image-m-54_1534366880759.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Diego Costa l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Marco Asensio v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Ronaldo thi  \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Bale vs Benzema. 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, b\u1ed9 ba n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c \u1ed5n.  Bale v\u00e0 Asensio m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Real Madrid, trong khi Benzema  c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n &ldquo;n\u1ed5 s\u00fang&rdquo;. \u1ede khu trung tuy\u1ebfn, Isco ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Luka Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c  \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean quen thu\u1ed9c Casemiro vs Toni Kroos. Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n  ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m \u1edf v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n b\u1edfi Modric v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua VCK World Cup  2018 qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Croatia m\u00e0 \u1edf ch\u1ed7: M\u1ea5y tu\u1ea7n qua, Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c  cho mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Bernabeu v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd nh\u1eb1m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed9ng Modric.</p>\r\n<p>V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Atletico Madrid, n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi HLV Diego  Simeone \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i n\u0103m nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Oblak, c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 Savic vs Godin, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n  v\u1ec7 Saul Niguez vs Koke v\u00e0 song s\u00e1t Griezmann vs Diego Costa. \u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi l\u1ed1i  ch\u01a1i, hai t\u00e2n binh Rodrigo vs Lemar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u1edbi tr\u00f4i qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n 30 gi\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf.  Trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Godin ph\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i v\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u00f3i quen, Diego Costa th\u1ec3  hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt, d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Sergio Ramos r\u1ed3i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n  \u1edf g\u00f3c h\u1eb9p, l\u00e0m tung n\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid. C\u00f3 b\u00e0n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb c\u1ef1c s\u1edbm, Atletico  c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 thi tri\u1ec3n s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m n\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u: ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Koke\" title=\"Koke\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/4F1F662A00000578-6064435-image-a-60_1534367851105.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Koke</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League t\u00edch c\u1ef1c pressing tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra  s\u1ee9c \u00e1p s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed7i khi c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 g\u1ea7n khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 th\u00ec v\u00f2ng v\u00e2y  c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e9p ch\u1eb7t, khi\u1ebfn cho huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t t\u1eed c\u1ee7a Champions League kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m  sao ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn n\u1ed5i khung th\u00e0nh Oblak d\u00f9 c\u1ea7m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng. M\u00e3i \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 17, h\u1ecd  m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee3t x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 Marcelo c\u0103ng ngang kh\u00f3  ch\u1ecbu, bu\u1ed9c Oblak ph\u1ea3i ra tay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 27, &quot;nh\u00e0 vua&quot; Champions League \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng  d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. T\u1eeb c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i, Bale t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng s\u00e2u v\u00e0o  khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 v\u00e0 Benzema lanh l\u1eb9 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fa m\u00e8o, ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u00f3n chu\u1ea9n \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3  \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh, \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi Oblak. Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau b\u00e0n g\u1ee1, Real  su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00f3 khi  Marco Asensio, sao tr\u1ebb ph\u1ea5t l\u00ean nh\u01b0 di\u1ec1u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0  th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn, b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1c lao xu\u1ed1ng x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Atletico r\u1ed3i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o  g\u00f3c ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n trong gang t\u1ea5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n sau pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Benzema v\u00e0 Atletico Madrid  d\u1ea7n chuy\u1ec3n sang ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 thay v\u00ec ung dung ki\u1ec1m t\u1ecfa. Cho \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1,  \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN v\u1eabn l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i song ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tung ra nh\u00e1t ki\u1ebfm  ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e2m tr\u1ecdng th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e3 h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m \u0111\u00e1ng gh\u00e9t. B\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p 2, hai \u0111\u1ed9i  gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergio Ramos\" title=\"Sergio Ramos\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/GettyImages-1017288384.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">S\u1ef1 nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Sergio Ramos</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>C\u00f3 v\u1ebb trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao, HLV Diego Simeone \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi  nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, gi\u00fap Atletico x\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0  l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00fang h\u00ecnh h\u00e0i \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c. V\u1eady l\u00e0, Los Blancos kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n tho\u1ea3i  m\u00e1i tung t\u1ea9y nh\u01b0 n\u1eeda sau hi\u1ec7p 1 l\u00fac h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3,  HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a Luka Modric v\u00e0o s\u00e2n nh\u1eb1m l\u00e0m t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o  c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</p>\r\n<p>S\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t khi l\u00e0m t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng  nh\u01b0 \u0111em l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 may m\u1eafn cho Real. Ph\u00fat 62, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i c\u01b0\u01a1ng quy\u1ebft ch\u1ec9 tay v\u00e0o ch\u1ea5m  ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n sau khi b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang v\u00e0o tay Juanfran \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng  v\u1edbi Benzema. Trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Sergio Ramos nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n v\u00e0  anh th\u1eeba b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh l\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean Atletico kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00fang b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t m\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i  v\u00f9ng l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 Real m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i chuy\u1ec3n sang th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1  - ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. S\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a v\u00e0 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a  HLV Zidane, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lopetegui k\u1ebf th\u1eeba. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng  ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Atletico phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Simeone. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, ph\u00fat 78, h\u00e0ng  th\u1ee7 \u00e1o tr\u1eafng thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0, \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eb7c cho Atletico \u0111e d\u1ecda v\u00e0 Angel Correa  chuy\u1ec1n cho Diego Costa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tung n\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n.</p>\r\n<p>T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean sau khi \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a, Atletico l\u1ea1i t\u00ecm v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00fang b\u1ea3n ng\u00e3 c\u00f2n Real kh\u00f4ng  d\u00e1m m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m \u00e0o l\u00ean trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1eeba r\u1ee7i ro. Th\u1ebf  l\u00e0, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tr\u00f4i qua \u00eam \u0111\u1ec1m v\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e0nh ch\u01a1i th\u00eam 30 ph\u00fat hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5. Real v\u1eabn  chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n tuy nhi\u00ean Atletico Madrid m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n  n\u1eefa cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 trong kh\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng..</p>\r\n<p>Ph\u00fat 98, trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee3t uy hi\u1ebfp hi\u1ebfm hoi, Thomas Partey \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng ra ph\u00eda sau  cho Saul Niguez b\u1eaft volley s\u1ea5m s\u00e9t, kh\u00f4ng cho Keylor Navas m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o. V\u00e0i  ph\u00fat sau, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh. Vitolo th\u1ea3  b\u00f3ng hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0o khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 cho Koke th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Navas. V\u1edbi  vi\u1ec7c Real \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n thua, HLV Lopetegui tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u  ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1948 s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n n\u00e0y trong tr\u1eadn ch\u00ednh  th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDanh d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t C1/Champions League kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p Real bu\u00f4ng  xu\u00f4i d\u00f9 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng. Tuy  nhi\u00ean ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e0nh b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0i ba c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i  nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 c\u00fa ra ch\u00e2n uy l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Modric b\u1ecb Oblak t\u00f3m g\u1ecdn.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Real Madrid 2-4 Atletico\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid 2-4 Atletico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Thong-so-Real-2-4-Atletico.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real Madrid 2-4 Atletico</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nV\u1eady l\u00e0, Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00fa hattrick \u0111o\u1ea1t danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u  \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 song h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi 3 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C1/Champions League cho ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i  v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Real: chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3  s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 th\u00ec s\u1ebd  ph\u1ea3i tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o t\u00e0i b\u1ed3i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng sao tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Lopetegui m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Trong khi  \u0111\u00f3, Atletico \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch  n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Simeone, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm \u1edf  TBN l\u1eabn ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nReal Madrid: </strong>Navas; Carvajal, Varane, Ramos, Marcelo; Casemiro (Dani Ceballos 76'), Kroos, Asensio (Luka Modric 57');  Bale, Isco (Lucas Vazquez 83'), Benzema.<br>\r\n<strong>Atletico Madrid: </strong>Oblak; Juanfran, Savic, Godin, Hernandez; Saul, Koke, Rodrigo (Vitolo 71'),  Lemar (Partey 90'+1); Griezmann (Angel Correa 58'), Diego Costa (Gimenez 109').\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>C\u00f4ng Minh (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5535","checkdouble":"194560"},{"date":"20:17 15/08","title":"Barca 3-0 Boca Juniors: C\u00fap Joan Gamper ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Camp Nou","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/de-bruyne-chan-thuong-nang-nghi-dai-han.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac, g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Cataluyna kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Argentina trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tranh c\u00fap Joan Gamper th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean. Si\u00eau sao Messi, t\u00e2n binh Malcom v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rafinha l\u00e0 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho Barca.</h2><h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: BARCA 3-0 BOCA JUNIORS\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/16/Barcelona-Vs-Boca-Juniors.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\u1ede 5 tr\u1eadn tranh chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean m\u00f9a h\u00e8 Joan Gamper (\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t theo t\u00ean c\u1ee7a  v\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch qu\u00e1 c\u1ed1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i Joan Gamper \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng s\u00e1ng l\u1eadp ra CLB Barcelona - PV)  tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u0103m 2018 , Barca \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, h\u1ecd v\u00f9i d\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed1i  th\u1ee7 Chapecoense c\u1ee7a Brazil 5 b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ee1. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, trong 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00f3i  tr\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalunya ghi t\u1edbi 25 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, trong khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 2  l\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Sampdoria 3-2 n\u0103m 2016.</p>\r\n<p>D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 ch\u1ec7ch cho\u1ea1c trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a H\u00e8 song khi c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t  tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Barca \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla 2-1 trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha  2018 nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ousmane Dembele.  HLV Valverde \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng xem tr\u1eadn tranh c\u00fap Joan Gamper 2018 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 giao  h\u1eefu v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t (v\u1eafng Alba, Luis Suarez,  Busquets) song v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Stegen,  c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 1 Pique vs Umtiti, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rakitic, ng\u00f4i sao Coutinho v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t  nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lionel Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, hai t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Arturo Vidal v\u00e0 Malcom c\u00f3  c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra m\u1eaft kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Camp Nou. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean  Vidal kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Barca sau v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb Bayern Munich. \u0110\u00fang v\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t  m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, hai b\u00ean nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng  v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a nhau nh\u1eb1m c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u hay nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Boca Juniors tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu Joan Gamper h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Barca vs Boca Juniors tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu Joan Gamper h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Truc-tiep-Barca-vs-Boca-Juniors-tran-dau-giao-huu-Joan-Gamper-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u0129 nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n, Barca l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 c\u01a1  h\u1ed9i uy hi\u1ebfp song ban \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u1edf  ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba. Ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 9, Messi b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1 g\u1ea7n khu v\u1ef1c 16m50  v\u00e0 g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn th\u1eb3ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Boca Juniors song ch\u00ednh M10 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u00fat  ph\u1ea1t tr\u00fang h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o ch\u1eafn b\u1eadt ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 17, Coutinho d\u1eabn b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e1p  s\u00e1t v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba Boca tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat tr\u00e1i ph\u00e1 nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Andrada  \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee9u thua cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Argentina. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i  c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n 1 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, Barca \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Malcom. T\u00e2n binh  sinh n\u0103m 1997 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, ung dung x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0  k\u1ebft th\u00fac b\u1eb1ng c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00ecm kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 hi\u1ec3m song v\u1eabn l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Boca b\u1edfi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n  \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMalcom \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh v\u00e0o m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u1edbi \u1edf Barca v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5u  \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ee3t giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Malcom \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh  s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng su\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Blaugrana khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u00e0n \"ph\u1ed7ng tay tr\u00ean\" ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c tr\u00ean  TTCN. Ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0 Malcom t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 bay \u0111\u1ebfn Italia \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi  Roma nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e9 m\u00e1y bay sang TBN gia nh\u1eadp Barca b\u1edfi  kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi c\u1ee7a g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Cataluyna.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e0ng gi\u00fap Barca ch\u01a1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u00e1c v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi. Ph\u00fat 30,  Boca Juniors c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t  g\u00f3c nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Stegen \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft g\u1ecdn c\u00fa lao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 7 Cristian  Pavon. Kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, s\u1ee9c \u00e9p m\u00e0 Barca t\u1ea1o ra v\u1ec1 khung th\u00e0nh Boca  c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n suy gi\u1ea3m nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 39, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 2. \u00dd \u0111\u1ed3 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng  cho Munir c\u1ee7a Messi b\u1ecb ch\u1eb7n l\u1ea1i song thi\u00ean t\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina v\u1eabn \u0111o\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c  b\u00f3ng, t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh d\u1eabn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m r\u1ed3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa t\u00e2ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt qua \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n  Boca \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thien tai Messi dong gop 1 ban o tran nay\" title=\"Thi\u00ean t\u00e0i Messi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/4F1EB43900000578-0-image-a-15_1534353359189.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thi\u00ean t\u00e0i Messi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Andrada m\u1edbi gips Boca tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi b\u00e0n  thua th\u1ee9 3 sau hai c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng  Argentina su\u00fdt c\u00f3 b\u00e0n r\u00fat ng\u1eafn c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m thay c\u00f4ng  vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Stegen sau c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Cardona. Pha s\u00fat b\u1ed3i k\u1ebf  ti\u1ebfp c\u0169ng b\u1ecb Umtiti ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n tr\u00ean v\u1ea1ch v\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao, Barca thay \u0111\u1ebfn 8 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n (ch\u1ec9 Munir, Miranda c\u00f9ng  Malcom \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i). Tuy v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n. Ph\u00fat 49, Munir  El Haddadi - ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1995 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh l\u00f2 La Masia danh ti\u1ebfng  nh\u01b0ng m\u1ea5y n\u0103m qua ph\u1ea3i \u0111i \"lang thang\" v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1  Barca - vung ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i s\u00fat ch\u00ecm t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng su\u00fdt tr\u00fang m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 53, Malcom ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng trong ch\u00e2n  tr\u00e1i k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u1edf s\u00e1t v\u1ea1ch 16m50 m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Boca kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, ch\u1eafc  ch\u1eafn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3 cho Barca. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nghi ng\u1edd g\u00ec, Malcom \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n  s\u1ebd l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Blaugrana m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong hi\u1ec7p 2  c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n ch\u1eadm l\u1ea1i, k\u00e9o theo s\u1ee9c h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3m theo. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Tevez \u0111\u00e3 qua th\u1eddi ho\u00e0ng kim t\u1eeb l\u00e2u v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng  khi \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ea1nh Luis Suarez. Ph\u00fat 67, Suarez nh\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 tinh t\u1ebf khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n  m\u00e0n ban b\u1eadt v\u1edbi Rafinha \u0111\u1ec3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7  m\u00f4n Boca v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e2ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111em v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3 cho Barca.  Rafinha c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o  anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Camp Nou b\u1edfi tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i sau khi  \u0111\u01b0a th\u00eam v\u1ec1 Arthur Melo v\u00e0 Vidal. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Rafinha kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan theo  di\u1ec7n cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 l\u1ebd ra \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh Milano n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t  kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 75, Carlos Tevez \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u00fa s\u00fat  t\u1eeb xa v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 ngang. Ph\u00fat 84, Lenglet - trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Sevilla m\u00f9a  h\u00e8 n\u00e0y - th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c nh\u01b0ng pha  tung ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee9u thua \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n kh\u00f4ng cho Lenglet  l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, l\u01b0\u1edbi Boca Juniors l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 4 rung l\u00ean sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ec7m l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Paco Alcacer nh\u01b0ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u00ec l\u1ed7i vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean Joan Gamper v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Camp Nou. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Barca. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nDANH S\u00c1CH XU\u1ea4T PH\u00c1T<br>\r\nBarcelona: Stegen, Pique, Umtiti, Miranda, Roberto, Vidal, Rakitic, Coutinho,  Messi, Malcom, Munir<br>\r\nBoca Juniors: Andrada, Buffarini, Goltz, Izquierdoz, Olaza, Nandez, Barrios,  Reynoso, Villa, Abila, Cardona<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f4ng Minh (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5534","checkdouble":"194556"},{"date":"20:33 15/08","title":"Real Madrid s\u1ebd chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Eriksen n\u1ebfu Modric ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/real-madrid-se-chi-200-trieu-euro-mua-eriksen-neu-modric-ra-di.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng cho s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Luka Modric, Real \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 \"Los Blancos\" d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi cho Eriksen l\u00e0 200 tri\u1ec7u euro.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o uy t\u00edn nh\u01b0 Gianluca Di Marzio kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Modric \u0111\u1ebfn Inter Milan \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. \u0110\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a \"Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018\", Real \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi l\u00ean t\u1edbi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n Eriksen g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda TTCN\u00a0h\u00e8 2018 (31/8).<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid s\u1ebd mua Eriksen n\u1ebfu Modric ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid s\u1ebd mua Eriksen n\u1ebfu Modric ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/Chi-100-trieu-bang,-PSG-muon-mua-Christian-Eriksen--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Anh ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i n\u00e0o. Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng mua b\u00e1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018. Th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea1i Anh l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 Eriksen ra \u0111i, \"G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\" ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Harry Kane, Eriksen l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Tottenham. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Eriksen ch\u01a1i 47 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn cho Spurs. Anh c\u00f3 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 13 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Kevin De Bruyne, Eriksen l\u00e0 \"s\u1ed1 10\" hay nh\u1ea5t Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 72 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 81 tri\u1ec7u euro. M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 Real d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra cho Eriksen v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1i t\u1eeb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal kh\u00f4ng mua b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 r\u1ea7m r\u1ed9 trong g\u1ea7n 4 n\u0103m qua. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng m\u00e0 \"Los Blancos\" th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 James Rodriguez t\u1eeb AS Monaco v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 88 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2014. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay, Real \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng chi qu\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u euro cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi ti\u00eau d\u00e8 s\u1ebbn nh\u01b0ng gi\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, Real l\u00e3i l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t kinh t\u1ebf. Trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018, Real m\u1edbi chi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 120 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 6 t\u00e2n binh. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \"Los Blancos\" \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 134 tri\u1ec7u euro sau khi \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 trong \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo sang Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c Real chi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u1ea3 thi. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng H\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5533","checkdouble":"194557"},{"date":"00:52 16/08","title":"Ramos ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Ronaldo \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/ramos-phan-phao-ronaldo-de-bao-ve-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh d\u00e0nh cho Juventus v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t d\u00ecm h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a CR7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt tai trung v\u1ec7 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay sau khi ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u0169 ph\u00e0ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ed1n c\u0169 Real Madrid v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 vinh quang tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergio Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1ec1 Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sergio Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1ec1 Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/ramos-phan-phao-ronaldo-de-bao-ve-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sergio Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Cristiano Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u1ea7m hi\u1ec3u qua nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u1edf th\u00e0nh Turin c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao 33 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh cho t\u00f4i khi Juventus l\u00e0 CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t Italia c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c b\u1edfi n\u00f3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c cho t\u00f4i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Ronaldo c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p \u1edf Bernabeu, n\u01a1i anh c\u0169ng t\u1eebng x\u1ea3y ra kh\u00f4ng \u00edt m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u1eeb HLV \u0111\u1ebfn ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady n\u00f3i g\u00ec th\u00ec n\u00f3i, ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n c\u1ee7a CR7 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nghe ch\u00fat n\u00e0o v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Sergio Ramos tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u n\u1ed5i anh \u1ea5y n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 ra sao, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong \u0111\u00f3. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u1eady th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady d\u00f9 c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng Ronaldo. Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ra \u0111i v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 h\u1ebft, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00f3 l\u00e0 Ronaldo. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin Real Madrid s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00ecnh n\u00e0y s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ai mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-372-194560.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-372-194560.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Real Madrid vs Atletico 02h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Real Madrid vs Atletico: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Real vs Atletico Madrid Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5532","checkdouble":"194572"},{"date":"06:46 16/08","title":"Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u: Diego Simeone \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/atletico-madrid-gianh-sieu-cup-chau-au-diego-simeone-lap-ky-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, HLV Diego Simeone \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u vinh quang nh\u1ea5t.</h2><h2>HLV Diego Simeone l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, Atletico Madrid m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7y su\u00f4n s\u1ebb v\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Ngo\u00e0i ra, chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u00fap HLV Diego Simeone l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Atletico.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u Diego Simeone l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Atletico Madrid gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u Diego Simeone l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/atletico-madrid-gianh-sieu-cup-chau-au-diego-simeone-lap-ky-luc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Diego Simeone l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c HLV gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f9ng Atletico Madrid.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCho \u0111\u1ebfn nay, \"El Cholo\" \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 th\u1ea3y 7 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng Atletico Madrid, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed1i Luis Aragones (6). HLV Simeone \u0111\u00e3 hai l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u (2012, 2018), 2 Europa League, 1 La Liga, 1 C\u00fap nh\u00e0 vua v\u00e0 1 Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>Danh hi\u1ec7u duy nh\u1ea5t HLV Simeone c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League danh gi\u00e1. El Cholo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng Atletico hai l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2014 v\u00e0 2016 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>Simeone c\u0169ng l\u00e0 HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Atletico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh C\u00fap nh\u00e0 vua, Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Julen Lopetegui<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div>G\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu m\u00f9a h\u00e8 nh\u01b0ng ngay trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eeba n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Real Madrid. Tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Los Blancos thua trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng sau Bernd Schuster n\u0103m 2007.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>Julen Lopetegui c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n n\u1eefa khi tr\u1edf HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u1ec3 thua 4 b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 60 n\u0103m. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 \u1edf Real Madrid l\u00e0 Michael Keeping trong tr\u1eadn thua Celta Vigo.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Atletico Madrid m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-372-194560.html\">Real Madrid 2-4 Atletico: Ma c\u0169 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t ma m\u1edbi, Atletico l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ramos-tran-an-courtois-truoc-man-ra-mat-lan-lon-cam-xuc-172-194531.html\">Ramos tr\u1ea5n an Courtois tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-atletico-madrid-tiet-lo-ly-do-tu-choi-gia-nhap-man-utd-172-194516.html\">Sao Atletico Madrid ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-valencia-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-atletico-madrid-180-194372.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Valencia chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Atletico Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-atletico-madrid-01-inter-milan-icc-2018-329-194290.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Atletico Madrid 0-1 Inter Milan (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5531","checkdouble":"194576"},{"date":"22:26 15/08","title":"Sao Man Utd tri \u00e2n Mourinho sau khi ra \u0111i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/sao-man-utd-tri-an-mourinho-sau-khi-ra-di.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daley Blind sau khi chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 H\u00e0 Lan kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Ajax Amsterdam.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau b\u1ed1n n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man Utd, Daley Blind quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 H\u00e0 Lan kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Ajax Amsterdam. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn kho\u1ea3ng 14 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb l\u00e2u khi trong v\u00f2ng hai n\u0103m nay \u1edf Old Trafford k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho, Blind kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 7 tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf Premier League (3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Blind r\u1eddi MU v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m \u01a1n HLV Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Blind r\u1eddi MU v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m \u01a1n HLV Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/blind.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Blind r\u1eddi MU v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m \u01a1n HLV Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 th\u00e1o ch\u1ea1y ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eady c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a Blind \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i Old Trafford nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec1m kh\u00edch v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tri \u00e2n Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ho\u0323c ho\u0309i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1\u0323c r\u00e2\u0301t nhi\u00ea\u0300u \u0111i\u00ea\u0300u t\u01b0\u0300 \u00f4ng \u00e2\u0301y, Jose Mourinho sinh ra \u0111\u00ea\u0309 gia\u0300nh chi\u00ea\u0301n th\u0103\u0301ng. 150 tr\u00e2\u0323n \u0111\u1ea5u va\u0300 4 danh hi\u00ea\u0323u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, khoa\u0309ng th\u01a1\u0300i gian ta\u0323i Manchester United th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u00e2\u0301t \u0111e\u0323p. Ca\u0309m \u01a1n ca\u0301c C\u0110V cu\u0303ng nh\u01b0 HLV Jose Mourinho.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Blind c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 g\u1eedi MU tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Instagram: \"L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o bi\u1ebft bao khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00ecnh Manchester United.\" <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao Man Utd tri \u00e2n Mourinho sau khi ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Sao Man Utd tri \u00e2n Mourinho sau khi ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Sao-Man-Utd-tri-an-Mourinho-sau-khi-ra-di-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Blind r\u1eddi MU v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m \u01a1n HLV Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\"\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho CLB l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi b\u1ec1 d\u00e0y truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed nh\u01b0 v\u1eady qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 n\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi 4 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 - c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u00e1c HLV, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 h\u1eadu c\u1ea7n, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00f4i ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp.\" <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\"T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u00ec t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, s\u1ebd m\u00e3i nh\u1edb 'Nh\u00e0 h\u00e1t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1'! Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 r\u1ed3i.\"<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5530","checkdouble":"194564"},{"date":"23:00 15/08","title":"Sao Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/sao-arsenal-tu-sanh-minh-voi-ronaldo-va-salah.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang sau h\u01a1n n\u1eeda n\u0103m c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Emirates v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 56 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cGia nh\u1eadp Arsenal trong th\u1eddi gian h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho t\u00f4i khi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 s\u00e1u th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 v\u0103n h\u00f3a Anh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d </em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cTh\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u00ec trong s\u00e1u th\u00e1ng \u0111\u00f3 khi m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 m\u1edbi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u x\u00e1n l\u1ea1n cho t\u00f4i, v\u1edbi m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.\u201d</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/aubameyang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Aubameyang c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, c\u00e1i \u201ckh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d m\u00e0 c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Gabon c\u1ee7a Dortmund n\u00f3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 th\u00edch nghi nhanh nh\u01b0 ch\u1edbp, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n khi anh ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 10 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong 12 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Premier League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea5y Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i thu th\u1eadp s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y nhanh nh\u01b0 Ronaldo hay Salah \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i ch\u1ea1y r\u1ea5t nhanh r\u1ed3i c\u01a1 m\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0 l\u1ebd s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.\u201d</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch xem nh\u1eefng b\u0103ng h\u00ecnh ghi l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 d\u1eef li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea1y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, b\u1edfi v\u00ec n\u00f3 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u.\u201d</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cN\u0103m nay trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eadn t\u1ed1c 37km/h v\u00e0 ngang b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Mbappe \u1edf World Cup 2018. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 29, th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i ch\u00fat n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2u.\u201d</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-van-de-cua-arsenal-sau-khi-chieu-mo-aubameyang-172-179372.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/3/goc-arsenal-thanh-hinh-voi-aubameyang-va-nhung-van-de.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-van-de-cua-arsenal-sau-khi-chieu-mo-aubameyang-172-179372.html\">G\u00f3c Arsenal: Th\u00e0nh h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Aubameyang v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Gabon, nh\u01b0ng song h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi bi\u1ebft bao h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5529","checkdouble":"194565"},{"date":"23:39 15/08","title":"Man Utd \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/man-utd-don-day-du-trong-phao-tro-lai-cuoi-tuan-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn hai ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Romelu Lukaku v\u00e0 Jesse Lingard \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n sung m\u00e3n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Brighton \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Brighton, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n l\u1ea1c quan h\u01a1n v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a th\u00eam hai ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU v\u1ec1 Lukaku v\u00e0 Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU v\u1ec1 Lukaku v\u00e0 Lingard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/HLV-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p hai v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u1edf Old Trafford, nh\u01b0ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t v\u00f4 duy\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Jesse Lingard v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Brighton vs MU \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19: \u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Pogba, Rashford v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, Lukaku, Lingard v\u00e0 Fellaini c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cho Man Utd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i sau hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, qua \u0111\u00f3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn quan tr\u1ecdng cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m n\u00e0y khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Tottenham.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/du-am-mu-20-leicester.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-20-leicester-172-194221.html\">Man Utd m\u1edf m\u00e0n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb: Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trung v\u1ec7? Kh\u00f4ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1!</span><br>\r\nPaul Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, Luke Shaw h\u1ed3i sinh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Eric Bailly v\u00e0 Victor Lindelof \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng MU 2-1 Leicester...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5528","checkdouble":"194567"},{"date":"23:54 15/08","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Arsenal b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/tan-hlv-arsenal-bi-chi-trich-hoc-doi-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Unai Emery b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Sam Allardyce quy k\u1ebft b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch n\u1eeda v\u1eddi v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Arsenal th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19 nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Manchester City, tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Guardiola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Guardiola h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-thua-cua-arsenal-truoc-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery tr\u1eadn Arsenal vs Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o Th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi sai l\u1ea7m chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery th\u00ec th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 dung th\u1ee9. \u0110\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p Sam Allardyce \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch k\u1ecbch li\u1ec7t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00ec c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn t\u1ef1 s\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Man City n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng pressing xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a HLV, anh \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City khi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 y nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft ch\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eeda v\u1eddi v\u00e0 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, n\u00f3 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Man City d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch pressing c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e1m \u0111\u00f4ng C\u0110V Arsenal tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i h\u00f2 reo khi Petr Cech quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c sang ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb \u00e1m \u1ea3nh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u1ee9ng nh\u1eafc v\u00e0 ngu ng\u1ed1c v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u01a1 ch\u1ee9. Khi n\u00e0o gi\u1ecfi nh\u01b0 Man City r\u1ed3i anh mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m g\u00ec th\u00ec l\u00e0m.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Arsenal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn derby th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-02-man-city-binh-moi-nhung-ruou-chua-moi-172-194363.html\">Arsenal 0-2 Man City: B\u00ecnh m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u ch\u01b0a m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City. V\u00e0 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5527","checkdouble":"194568"},{"date":"00:24 16/08","title":"Man City nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 De Bruyne","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/Kevin-De-Bruyne-1003773.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn 2-3 th\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfp theo.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u00ec Kevin De Bruyne v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t s\u00e2n c\u1ecf v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Manchester City v\u00e0 theo nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t ra t\u1eeb Etihad, c\u00e1c C\u0110V s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i th\u00eam r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u n\u1eefa m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Kevin-De-Bruyne-1003773.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n cho Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, De Bruyne \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 theo chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Kristof Terreur, c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn 2-3 th\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfp theo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ebfu nguy c\u01a1 n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt, Man City s\u1ebd t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf qu\u00e1 n\u1eeda l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, De Bruyne s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Premier League c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Champions League v\u00e0 League Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Pep Guardiola s\u1ebd hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u nguy\u1ec7n c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 7/10 g\u1eb7p Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng Man City tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng trong n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, De Bruyne ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Man City v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u1edbi bi\u1ebft bao k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u00f4 ti\u1ec1n kho\u00e1ng h\u1eadu b\u1ecb x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/de-bruyne-tu-thang-nhoc-uong-buong-den-mot-ngoi-sao-172-171225.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/21/kevin-de-bruyne-tu-thang-nhoc-uong-buong-den-mot-ngoi-sao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/de-bruyne-tu-thang-nhoc-uong-buong-den-mot-ngoi-sao-172-171225.html\">Kevin De Bruyne: T\u1eeb th\u1eb1ng nh\u00f3c \u01b0\u01a1ng b\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ai bi\u1ebft Kevin De Bruyne t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ea9u c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e0n anh David Silva hay Fernandinho, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u01b0\u1eddi x\u00f2a r\u1ed3i n\u00f3i: Th\u1eb1ng nh\u00f3c \u0111\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5526","checkdouble":"194571"},{"date":"15:42 15/08","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Sterling gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch h\u00ecnh x\u0103m m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7y \u00fd ngh\u0129a","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/tien-dao-sterling-giai-thich-hinh-xam-moi-day-y-nghia.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5525","checkdouble":"194543"}]}